body.p: This is a metabolism model of Human glucose metabolism in SBML format.
This model is based on the model described in the article:

div.a: Quantifying the contribution of the liver to glucose homeostasis: a detailed kinetic model of human hepatic glucose metabolism.

body.div: König M., Bulik S., Holzhütter HG.
